## Point cloud 생성

### 배열로 생성



{:.input_area}
```python
pc_array = np.array([[1, 2, 3], [3, 4, 5]], dtype=np.float32)
print(pc_array)
```


{:.output_stream}
```
[[1. 2. 3.]
 [3. 4. 5.]]

```



{:.input_area}
```python
#방법 1
pc = pcl.PointCloud(pc_array)
print(pc)
```


{:.output_stream}
```
<PointCloud of 2 points>

```



{:.input_area}
```python
#방법 2
pc = pcl.PointCloud()
pc.from_array(pc_array)
print(pc)
```


{:.output_stream}
```

```
